{"content": "I need to multiply 322 \u00d7 248 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 322\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 2\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 243 + 18 + 2 = 263\u2081\u2080\n- 248\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070 = 2\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 162 + 36 + 8 = 206\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 263 \u00d7 206 = 54,178\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 54178 \u00f7 9 = 6019 r 7\n- 6019 \u00f7 9 = 668 r 7\n- 668 \u00f7 9 = 74 r 2\n- 74 \u00f7 9 = 8 r 2\n- 8 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 8\n\nReading from bottom to top: **82277\u2089**\n\n82277", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 323}